            <div class="article">
            <h1><br /><a href="http://unideal.net/wordpress/?p=374">Pike&#8217;s Peak or Bust &#8211; Apple Farmer Racing 2010</a></h1>

            <div class="clr "></div>
            <ul class="extendspost" style="border-top:none">
                <li style="text-align:right;border-top:none;border-bottom:none"> <strong>Jun 15th, 2010</strong></li>

            </ul>

            <p class="tags"><a href="http://unideal.net/wordpress/?tag=pikes-peak" rel="tag">pikes peak</a>, <a href="http://unideal.net/wordpress/?tag=volvo" rel="tag">volvo</a></p>

            <div class="content">
            <p><a href="http://applefarmerracing.com/"><img class="alignright" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4015/4687743113_2213ea0076_o.png" alt="" width="276" height="380" /></a>Apple Farmer Racing took on the 88th running of the Pike&#8217;s Peak International Hillclimb in June 2010. Pike&#8217;s Peak International Hillclimb is the second oldest motor sports event in the United States:  a 12.4 mile, 156 turn race through my butts to Pike&#8217;s Peak&#8217;s 14,110&#8242; summit. The race forces competitors to climb over a mile and race through sheer dropoffs and dangerous switchbacks. </p>
<p>We were the only 4 cylinder car to finish in a large vintage class of American v8&#8217;s. We&#8217;re also the first Volvo in the race since 1958. Our final time of 15:15 wasn&#8217;t quite where we wanted to be but we chalk it up to a rookie attempt and are already redeveloping the car for next year&#8217;s event.</p>
<p><a href="http://applefarmerracing.com"><img class="aligncenter  size-medium wp-image-378" title="tshirtlogo_back" src="http://unideal.net/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirtlogo_back-300x30.png" alt="tshirtlogo_back" width="317" height="31" srcset="http://unideal.net/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirtlogo_back-300x30.png 300w, http://unideal.net/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirtlogo_back-1024x102.png 1024w, http://unideal.net/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/tshirtlogo_back.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 317px) 100vw, 317px" /></a> </p>
<p></p>
            <br /><br />
            <div class="solidline margintop"></div>
            

